gomodel:SYNGO_3950  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig 2: LTP is depressed in CA1 and CA3 regions of 1-month-old Jnk2-/- mice\nFig 4: reduced slope of the presynaptic volley-fEPSP curve in Jnk2-/- mice, Decreased PTP\nFig 5: Increased Synaptic fatigue during HFS (100Hz, 40 pulses) in the presence of 100um D-APV leads the authors to conclude that there are differences in the depletion process of the docked vesicles.. Experimental description: M&M: Jnk2 -/- mice and control wild-type mice used in this study have been described previously (Sabapathy et al. 1999a). All mice were of the C57B6/129 genetic background." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9900-4233" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
